description.plain:
Victoria Loren Kelly was born on December 14th, 1992 in Wildomar, California.

She began making and posting music videos to YouTube when she was 14 and even auditioned for American Idol when she was 16 – later being disqualified.

In 2012 she released her first EP entitled Handmade Songs by Tori Kelly. In 2013 she was signed to Capitol Records and shortly after released her second EP, Foreword.

Her debut album, entitled Unbreakable Smile, was released on June 23rd, 2015, then re-released on January 29, 2016, with two new tracks. It reached number 2 on the Billboard 200.

On September 14, 2018, she released her sophomore album Hiding Place, which received two Grammys for Best Gospel Album and Best Gospel Performance/Song at the 61st Grammy Awards.

Her Acoustic Sessions Tour was announced on January 28, 2019, to promote her album, Inspired by True Events along with the lead single, Change Your Mind which was released January 25th. The second single, Sorry Would Go a Long Way, was released on June 28th, 2019. The album itself was released on August 9th, 2019.

songs.title: Paper Hearts

description.plain:
“Paper Hearts” is the fourth track of Tori Kelly’s Foreword EP.

The song focuses on a past relationship. Tori reminisces about the good and the bad memories of relationship through old photographs.

songs.full_title: I Was Made for Loving You by Tori Kelly (Ft. Ed Sheeran)
songs.title: I Was Made for Loving You
songs.title_with_featured: I Was Made for Loving You (Ft. Ed Sheeran)

description.plain:
“I Was Made For Loving You” is the seventh track off of Tori Kelly’s debut album, Unbreakable Smile.

The song is about a girl who is worried about entering a relationship with a man (portrayed in the song by Ed Sheeran) she is in love with. She knows nothing about the man but she feels it is a destined love. The man feels the same as he reassures her and they begin their relationship despite the uncertainty.



The use of string instruments, tambourine, percussion shakers, and storytelling makes the song reminiscent of folk pop.

songs.full_title: Dear No One by Tori Kelly
songs.title: Dear No One

description.plain:
“Dear No One” is the second song of five on Tori Kelly’s Foreword. Tori explains how she hasn’t found that special someone yet; However, this song is dedicated to her future love interest when that person comes along.

This song is also the first bonus track on her debut album Unbreakable Smile.
